## Use-cases

> One `### UC-<n> — <title>` per case. All 7 fields mandatory.
> `Tier` rule (mechanical, ADR-012): touches DataSource / real driver / network / build ⇒ `integration` or `contract`, NEVER `unit`.
> `Observable` = what to observe (assertion target), NOT the test code.

